    "He predicted that socialism would result in an era of collectivist art in his 1913 book <em>Der nackte Mensch in der Kunst aller Zeiten und V\u00f6lker</em>.": [],
    "He continued to be a leading exponent in the expressionist movement.": [],
    "Hausenstein, and fellow SPD member <a href=\"/behnea\">Adolf Behne</a>, were the only critics to promote Expressionism from a left-wing point of view (Werkmeister).": [
