    "His introductory books on artists were some of the most well-researched of the genre.": [],
    "His <em>Giotto</em>, for example, examines the theories of <a href=\"/rumohrk\">Karl Friedrich von Rumohr</a> thought <a href=\"/burckhardtj\">Jacob Burckhardt</a> on the artist in a thoughtful discussion of historiography.": [],
    "Although Hausenstein continued to write about modern art in later years, his views were always followed the model of decline and dissolution.": [
